item.title: CVE-2023-27905|2024-08-02T12:23:30.405Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20update-center2
item.description: Jenkins update-center2 3.13 and 3.14 renders the required Jenkins core version on plugin download index pages without sanitization, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers able to provide a plugin for hosting.
